# Push After Every Update

After making code changes in this repository:

1. Commit with a concise message describing why the change was made.
2. Push to `origin` on the current branch immediately — do not wait for the user to ask.
3. Only skip push if the user explicitly says not to push, or if there are no changes to commit.

Do not push secrets (.env, credentials, etc.).
